(524, 1, '2018-01-14 11:28:25', '2018-01-14 05:28:25', 'Progya is a Community of practice and we therefore encourage you to interact with other members. You can use the  “private message\" option to connect with other members of Progya Community.\n<h3>Private messages</h3>\nSince Progya is a community of practice, all our registered members have the option of connecting with each other by sending private messages to other users. You have to be logged in in order to be able to use this function.\n<h3>Managing private messages</h3>\nYou will be notified about new messages received in Progya :\n<ul>\n 	<li>Via email</li>\n 	<li>When logging in Progya with your username and password</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How to send a private message</h3>\nIn the profile of each member you can find the menu: Message>send\nWrite a new message in your Messages section and then send.\n\nNB: to send messages to other members, you have to add the USERNAME of the recipient(s), NOT the Name or email', 'Connect With Members', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '423-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-01-14 11:28:25', '2018-01-14 05:28:25', '', 423, 'http://localhost/kmp/?p=524', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
